sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant Nginx
    participant Gateway

    Note over Admin,Gateway: Admin has already logged in.

    Admin           ->>  Nginx          :   HTTP GET http://libofalex.com/newbook
    Nginx           ->>  Gateway        :   HTTP GET http://server-gateway/api/v1/auth/verify/hasRole?=<<UserRole>> <br/>(with Access Token)
    Note over Gateway: REF: GF-05 User Role Verification Flow
    Gateway         -->> Nginx          :   HTTP 200 OK
    Nginx           -->> Admin          :   HTTP 200 OK newbook.html
